MODULE
     mod_actions - Filetype/method-based script execution.

DESCRIPTION
     This module runs CGI scripts whenever a file  of  a  certain
     type or HTTP method (See RFC 1945) is requested. The follow-
     ing config directives are described:

       * Action

       * Script


