     _S_y_n_t_a_x: _A_c_t_i_o_n mime-type cgi-script
      _D_e_f_a_u_l_t: - None -
      _M_o_d_u_l_e: mod_actions(3)

     _A_c_t_i_o_n adds an action,  which  will  activate  a  _c_g_i-_s_c_r_i_p_t
     whenever a file of a certain _m_i_m_e-_t_y_p_e is requested. It pro-
     pagates the URL and file  path  of  the  requested  document
     using   the   standard  CGI  _P_A_T_H__I_N_F_O  and  _P_A_T_H__T_R_A_N_S_L_A_T_E_D
     environment variables.

     Examples:

     Action text/plain /cgi-bin/log_and_deliver_text
     Action home-grown/mime-type1 /~bob/do_special_stuff

